{
  "name": "Text to Video - Wan 2.2 TI2V-5B (Low Quality)",
  "author": "InvokeAI",
  "description": "Text-to-video generation with Wan 2.2 TI2V-5B. Produces an MP4 of `num_frames` frames at `fps` frames-per-second (defaults: 81 frames @ 16 FPS = ~5 s, 720p ~1248x704). The output lands in the gallery alongside images and plays inline in the viewer.",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "contact": "",
  "tags": "wan2.2, text to video, video",
  "notes": "This workflow needs the Wan 2.2 TI2V-5B model. Each InvokeAI install assigns its own internal model IDs, so the model fields are left blank -- select these in the form after loading:\n\nMain Model node:\n- Main Model: Wan 2.2 TI2V-5B (Q4_K_M GGUF recommended for <=16 GB VRAM)\n- Transformer (Low Noise): leave empty (TI2V-5B is a single-expert model)\n- VAE: Wan 2.2 TI2V-5B VAE\n- T5 Encoder: Wan T5 Encoder (UMT5-XXL)\n\nDefault output is 720p (~1248x704); reduce the \"Ideal Dimensions\" preset to 480p for less VRAM.",
